General.Name: Millbank Mining Corp.
General.Description: Millbank Mining Corp. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in British Columbia, Canada. The company explores for copper deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the Arthur Lake property comprising two claim units that covers an area of 543 hectares located in central British Columbia. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
General.Address: 503-905 West Pender Street, Vancouver, BC, Canada, V6C 1L6
